snippet.textDisplay: Shuza Haider ji.....aap itne zda khubsurat dikhte ho or aapki awas itni zda , itni zda achhi hai, ye mje is song ke bad pta lga hai. Ap achhe lyricist bhi ho, ye baat apko bilkul alag krti hai dusron se.Shuru mein ye normal song hi lga Tha lekin jse jse 1-2 dfa sunta gya isko, lga ki kitna hd se zda pyara song hai. Apki awaz bahut psnd ayi. Actually heavy voice waale singer mje bahut psnd hn (bcz meri awz kafi heavy hai, but mera singing se vaasta nhi hai koi, mai bahut be-sura hun). Please accept Lots of love from other side of the border. Ishwar aapko bahut khush rkhe or apki Sundar awaz or compositions ase hi hme milti rhe.

snippet.textDisplay: My wife left me due to some materialistic reasons since more than 2 years.  This song hits me directly and I am unable to express my whole feelings.  I cannot forget her ever in my life. This song starts with a soulful voice and mesmerizing lyrics. Tau Aao na Bawaray shakes my body n soul. Music sings in this song.  Tu hi bta kiya karun…..kahan jaun mein…teray jaisa koi kahan se laun mein…..tau aao na Bawaray.  Tum yad aye aur tmharay sath zamanay yad aye. Endless/meaningful Poetry. At 5.34 Aima Baig takes this track to another level which is out of this world with powerful pitch of her voice.  Laut aao tum….Mera har pal jal raha hai…aa bhi jao tum….tanha hun mein yahan. Truly my internal feelings. All musicians are the Magicians.  Ahad Niyani also sing a piece along with. I love this masterpiece production Wholeheartedly.
